        "created_at": "2018-09-27T16:25:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Also love that you did this pairing, Carlos, thanks for sharing with us.  I have a marked Grenache aversion\u2013except when it comes to Rayas and Beaucastel\u2026Rayas because I have found it to be so luminous and beautiful, Beaucastel because, like Robert, I love the mourvedre component.</p>\n<p>Salud,</p>\n<p>Mike</p>",
