        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/8baadc/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-09-28T09:17:21.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>1989 &amp; 1990 Rayas are both among the 5 best wines I\u00b4ve ever tasted. Hard to decide which is the winner  <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/c/ce2642e7caade9035e3a3b13c8b8d2b3ddb2b4c9.gif\" width=\"43\" height=\"54\" alt=\"flirtysmile\" title=\"[flirtysmile.gif]\"><br>\n(and imho clearly above Beaucastel)</p>",
